{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, it took approximately 120 h per annotator to annotate all the 400 biomedical articles.",
    "BERN-annotated PubMed AbstractsDue to the small size of our manually annotated corpus, online machine automatically annotated corpora were also downloaded and trained prior to fine-tuning on our manual annotations, as is discussed later in 2.2.1 Section.",
    "It is worth noting that the downloaded corpora and our manual annotations should not be overlapped to prevent data leakage between two phases of fine-tuning.",
    "The selected dataset was 549,587 BERN-annotated PubMed abstracts in the year of 1978 and 1979 corresponding to pubmed19n0001.",
    "json ~ pubmed19n0018.json [29]."
  ]
}